  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Will the price of wheat flour be reduced?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Trade and Consumer Protection Minister Nalin Fernando said that a decision will be taken today (05) regarding the price of wheat flour.",
        "The minister also said that he will discuss with the bakery owners about the price of wheat flour and related bread.",
        "The minister also said that a report has been requested from the manufacturing companies regarding the price of wheat flour currently being sold to consumers.",
        "Meanwhile, following the increase in the price of Gotha flour, the price of pan has been increased by Rs 300 and the price of other snacks has also been increased. (R)"
      ],
